    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Objective: F.E.A.S.T</strong> is a time survival game with some roguelite elements, and an interesting movement system <strong>(pick up and drop)</strong>. The world is being taken over by demon-possessed fruits and it's the job of the agency to save humanity from the underworld's reign.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277390/extras/8321f488d4728e5d499604beaa981d65.apng?t=1753246588\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277390/extras/8321f488d4728e5d499604beaa981d65.poster.avif?t=1753246588\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What To Expect:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide range of enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Playable Characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ Weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ Items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of crispy weapon synergies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An... interesting... story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weird music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrible pixel art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fun time!</p></li></ul>",
